OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776999825
OL,3,CMartin Compston urges voters to back
OL,4,CSNP to 'keep Farage out of Scotland'
OL,6,FMartin Compston has urged Scots to
OL,7,Fback the SNP to keep Nigel Farage's
OL,8,F"toxic politics out of Scotland" as he
OL,9,Faccused Scottish Labour of wanting to
OL,10,Fdo a deal with Reform.
OL,12,FThe Line Of Duty Star has backed John
OL,13,FSwinney as First Minister and called
OL,14,Ffor people to "unite behind" his party.
OL,16,FThe pair will campaign for the SNP in
OL,17,FInverclyde on Friday, the home of both
OL,18,FMr Compston and Lord Malcom Offord,
OL,19,Fthe leader of Reform UK Scotland.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@`O]vD@OOUvD@\O]
