OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776999825
OL,3,CMartin Compston urges voters to back
OL,4,CSNP to 'keep Farage out of Scotland'
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of his visit, Mr
OL,7,FCompston accused Mr Farage of seeking
OL,8,Fto shrink Scotland's budget and its
OL,9,FParliament and said he would privatise
OL,10,Fthe NHS "if he got half the chance".
OL,12,FAlong with the First Minister, the
OL,13,FScottish actor claimed Labour wants to
OL,14,Fwork with Reform after the election.
OL,26,@rD@IOUrD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
