FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776999825
OL,3,CMartin Compston urges voters to back
OL,4,CSNP to 'keep Farage out of Scotland'
OL,6,FLord Offord, along with other senior
OL,7,Ffigures in Reform UK Scotland, have
OL,8,Faccused Scottish Labour leader Anas
OL,9,FSarwar of approaching them and
OL,10,Foffering to work with them to kick out
OL,11,Fthe SNP after the election. Labour has
OL,12,Fdenied this and accused Lord Offord of
OL,13,Flying.
OL,15,FMr Compston, a vocal pro-independence
OL,16,Fsupporter, is backing the SNP in the
OL,17,FScottish Parliament elections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776999825
OL,3,CMartin Compston urges voters to back
OL,4,CSNP to 'keep Farage out of Scotland'
OL,6,FHe said: "Nigel Farage isn't
OL,7,Finterested in Scotland ` he wants to
OL,8,Fcut our budget, shrink our Parliament
OL,9,Fand would privatise our NHS if he got
OL,10,Fhalf the chance. We should have none
OL,11,Fof it.
OL,13,F"And the fact that Labour are willing
OL,14,Fto work with him shows just how far
OL,15,Fthey have fallen.
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776999825
OL,3,CMartin Compston urges voters to back
OL,4,CSNP to 'keep Farage out of Scotland'
OL,6,F"On May 7th, the way to keep Farage's
OL,7,Ftoxic politics out of Scotland is for
OL,8,Fpeople to unite behind the SNP ` and
OL,9,Fthe way to lock Farage out of Scotland
OL,10,Ffor good is by becoming an independent
OL,11,Fcountry."
OL,13,FIn a joint call, Mr Swinney, who will
OL,14,Fvisit Greenock Morton Football Club,
OL,15,Fsaid it was the SNP that offered Scots
OL,16,Fan alternative to Reform, which is
OL,17,Fcurrently battling Scottish Labour for
OL,18,Fsecond place in the polls.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
