FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776999825
OL,3,CMartin Compston urges voters to back
OL,4,CSNP to 'keep Farage out of Scotland'
OL,6,FThe SNP leader said: "I am absolutely
OL,7,Fclear ` I will have nothing to do with
OL,8,FNigel Farage, his man in Scotland Lord
OL,9,FOfford or Reform UK.
OL,11,F"Their politics are dangerous and the
OL,12,Fvery idea that they could have power
OL,13,Fand influence in Parliament after the
OL,14,Felection will be really concerning to
OL,15,Fpeople across the country.
OL,17,F"We know what Reform would mean for
OL,18,FScotland and the fact that Labour are
OL,19,Fwilling to work with them after the
OL,20,Felection shows just how desperate they
OL,21,Fhave become.
OL,26,@nD@VOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776999825
OL,3,CMartin Compston urges voters to back
OL,4,CSNP to 'keep Farage out of Scotland'
OL,6,F"That is why we need an SNP majority
OL,7,Fat this election which will unlock the
OL,8,Ffresh start of independence and lock
OL,9,FNigel Farage out of power in Scotland.
OL,11,F"And I am asking people to unite
OL,12,Fbehind the SNP for a government under
OL,13,Fmy experienced, reliable leadership
OL,14,Fthat is always on Scotland's side."
OL,16,FScottish Labour said it was
OL,17,Fdisappointed in the Sweet Sixteen
OL,18,Factor.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
