FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776999825
OL,3,CMartin Compston urges voters to back
OL,4,CSNP to 'keep Farage out of Scotland'
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the party said:
OL,7,F"The fact that the SNP are peddling
OL,8,Fthe lies of Reform demonstrates just
OL,9,Fhow far they have fallen.
OL,11,F"While he has made a career out of
OL,12,Freading other people's lines, it is
OL,13,Fcertainty disappointing to see Martin
OL,14,FCompston parroting the SNP's absolute
OL,15,Fnonsense.
OL,17,F"Perhaps if he takes a closer look at
OL,18,Ftheir dismal campaign of
OL,19,Fmisinformation and smears, he will see
OL,20,Fhow utterly desperate they have become
OL,21,Fand distance himself from the SNP".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU}D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
