PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776999825
OL,3,CMartin Compston urges voters to back
OL,4,CSNP to 'keep Farage out of Scotland'
OL,6,FScottish Labour deputy leader Jackie
OL,7,FBaillie said it was "dishonest" for
OL,8,Fthe First Minister to say he would
OL,9,Fhave nothing to do with Reform "when
OL,10,Fthe SNP are ploughing money behind a
OL,11,FLord Offord advert promoting his lies
OL,12,Fabout Anas Sarwar".
OL,14,FShe said: "Reform launched racist
OL,15,Fattack ads against Anas Sarwar during
OL,16,Fthe Hamilton, Larkhall and Stonehouse
OL,17,Fby-election, and have signalled they
OL,18,Fwould be prepared to use them again.
OL,26,@oD@UOUoD@_O]qD@`OUtD@RO]vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
