OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776999825
OL,3,CMartin Compston urges voters to back
OL,4,CSNP to 'keep Farage out of Scotland'
OL,6,F"This is not a serious or credible
OL,7,Fparty. Scottish Labour has been
OL,8,Fabsolutely clear that there will be no
OL,9,Fpacts, no deals, and no coalitions `
OL,10,Fwe are going flat out to win this
OL,11,Felection because Scotland needs change.
OL,13,F"John Swinney and the SNP should look
OL,14,Fthemselves in the mirror and consider
OL,15,Fwhether their desperate attempts to
OL,16,Fjoin forces with Reform to try and
OL,17,Fsmear Anas Sarwar is morally the right
OL,18,Fthing to do."
OL,20,FReform UK Scotland has been approached
OL,21,Ffor comment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
